{"tid":2290573,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳42歲陳鍵鋒腦患遺傳病大受打擊　將退出娛圈一心傳教","createTime":"2020-11-18T06:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T14:15:00.000Z","uid":212249,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e5cb7c6f8b950a35d55c60caea4c3f89afe5438c","tid":2290573,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201116/405059190868938752642391.jpeg/oYv1Zp4LjeOaf8yzNIXlkz5tm0BQz6z_AGib-wBom_s?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201116%2F405059190868938752642391.jpeg%2FoYv1Zp4LjeOaf8yzNIXlkz5tm0BQz6z_AGib-wBom_s%3Fv%3Dw960&h=40ef8e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現年42歲的陳鍵鋒（Sammul）在無綫拍過不少大熱劇集，曾為一線小生，備受無綫力捧。他於2010年北上內地發展，久未在港露面，自去年底拍完網絡電影《封神榜大破萬仙陣》後，亦未有再接任何新劇或綜藝節目。自日前廖碧兒 （Bernice）分享兩人聚會合照，觀眾才能看見已經散發濃烈中佬味的陳鍵鋒近照。<br />\n<br />\n近日有報道指，陳鍵鋒前年到泰國做身體檢查後，發現患上遺傳病，腦部天生缺少了一條血管。驚悉患病的陳鍵鋒人生觀從此改變。身為虔誠基督徒的陳鍵鋒稱受「天父的召喚」，早前決定修讀為期4年的遙距神學學士課程。日前有傳他攻讀完學士及碩士後，將退出娛樂圈，一心一意去傳教，以自身經歷啟發他人。<br />\n<br />\n陳鍵鋒接受傳媒訪問時僅簡單回應，自己正在努力工作和努力讀書。好友王賢誌則回覆傳媒稱，相信陳鍵鋒是為專心讀書而休息。"},{"pid":"239be16e872ee7dfc0b39ed5f7adee998378c3f3","tid":2290573,"uid":204306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"Gay佬都係基督徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf73751d5142bdb245b0f87d7adfd19c5b89c80","tid":2290573,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:48:36.000Z","msg":"咁就開心喇 神想召見佢"},{"pid":"b791c7c03bc935c77d9cc4131879abbdad0f2e9f","tid":2290573,"uid":103230,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"係一個咩病<br />\n40歲先發現冇左條血管<br />\n但又生存左咁耐<br />\n咁對佢咩影響"},{"pid":"148222fa13ee340c435d8b013704df07acafd584","tid":2290573,"uid":17110,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"李柏翹唔做狗去傳教<br />\n依個結局真係估唔到"},{"pid":"04e88bfb8b4fb6e919b78dd3812b7387328b0438","tid":2290573,"uid":164730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:54:30.000Z","msg":"廖碧兒幅圖keep得幾好<br />\n話30我都信"},{"pid":"05e12fb2d505fd8a82fbe3df6296a1daea3d33be","tid":2290573,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:59:41.000Z","msg":"又封神榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大陸而家啲無新意到咁<br />\n一係翻炒古典小說<br />\n一係家庭劇 抗日劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5245bbdbeea225f03bae458a6dc4b86536eb0a1","tid":2290573,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"239be16e872ee7dfc0b39ed5f7adee998378c3f3","tid":2290573,"uid":204306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"Gay佬都係基督徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:01:33.000Z","msg":"自己 搞鳩自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e304fd7cdec8c55dc7315d2f5aac407fb8fefcc0","tid":2290573,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"239be16e872ee7dfc0b39ed5f7adee998378c3f3","tid":2290573,"uid":204306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"Gay佬都係基督徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T07:09:57.000Z","msg":"Gay篤桃🍑"},{"pid":"3c8a63bd62a713bb55f2a5caf6e265a711f87c4c","tid":2290573,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":